<title>UK: Kalamazoo says in talks for possible offer.</title>
<headline>Kalamazoo says in talks for possible offer.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-06-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Britain's Kalamazoo Computer Group Plc said on Tuesday it was in discussions which might or might not lead to an offer for the company.</p>
<p>&quot;The board is in discussion which may or may not lead to an offer being made for the whole of the issued share capital of the company,&quot; it said in reaction to recent press speculation and subsequent movement in its share price.  </p>
<p>The share price of Kalamazoo gained further ground on Tuesday and was marked up 14 1/2 pence at 93 1/2.</p>
